{"tid":1970133,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Party場地協會對未獲政府資助表示非常失望","createTime":"2020-04-13T02:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T04:39:29.000Z","uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"10b7b7aa620fc9f554a32a5f29ee7bbe5bb830c6","tid":1970133,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:18:54.000Z","msg":"政府在第二輪防疫抗疫基金中，對多類早前被勒令關閉的場所，包括酒吧、健身中心等提供額外資助，但沒有列明資助派對房間。香港派對場地協會會長林漢然在一個電台節目中表示非常失望，說行業在社會運動已經受影響，疫情下生意再遭重創，特別是出現發生在派對房間的「打邊爐家族」事件後，部分地區的房間生意更急跌約九成。<br />\n<br />\n對於政務司長張建宗表示，相信很多派對房間持有食肆牌照，林漢然批評說法不符行業實況，又指中小企融資計劃幫助非常有限，如果經濟持續不景，可能有八至九成派對房間需要結業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1280449&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1280449%26csid%3D261_341&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=4eec890b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1280449&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"b2c15e6b760c97ca4b241531c6bbc5b6e6da382f","tid":1970133,"uid":187957,"like":13,"dislike":4,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:19:18.000Z","msg":"根本就唔應該存在"},{"pid":"73631997e6432d712c0c3c18dda420b4d5e62ff5","tid":1970133,"uid":29675,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:22:30.000Z","msg":"而家差唔多個個行業都出黎訴苦搏R資助"},{"pid":"6a8c40e9a63edee5c0cdb23ff2375ec7acad8faf","tid":1970133,"uid":212626,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:22:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nDAoTJQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnDAoTJQ.jpg&h=65e950de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"197f2abd0672176271f174985ac7f1b50964d9ef","tid":1970133,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T02:27:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2e214019dd6